result.title: Invitation to HackerEarth CodeMonk — Trees
result.content:
Hi everyone!

HackerEarth CodeMonk Trees challenge will go live today at 21:00 IST (check your timezone here).

The challenge will have 5 algorithmic tasks to be solved in 3 hours. Problems are based on Binary Trees and Binary Search Trees. You will receive points for every test case your solution passes — so you can get some points with partial solutions as well.

See you on the leaderboard!!.
